","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Brian Britt","primary":true}}]}},"person_74193_translations":{"at":1773688729608,"data":{"id":74193,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Sam Lee Chan-Sam (Chinese: 李燦森) is a Hong Kong  actor born on September 27, 1975. He started his film career when he was first spotted by director Fruit Chan who cast him in the 1997 film Made in Hong Kong (香港製造). In 2002, he appeared the Japanese film Ping Pong (ピンポン) as one of the contestants. Sam Lee is best known for the role of Sha Jang in the epic 2002 television series The Monkey King: Quest for the Sutra (齊天大聖孫悟空). Outside of his film career, he is a seasonal member of a metal/hip-hop band Lazy Mutha Fucka (LMF) where he is the rapper. Sam Lee is also known as DJ Becareful.","name":"Sam Lee","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"李灿森，香港电影演员。曾演出的电影包括《香港制造》、《特警新人类》、《龙咁威2003》、《狗咬狗》等。他曾是乐队LMF的成员，并曾跟Ketchup合作；现时也是唱片骑师，代号DJ Be Careful。","name":"李灿森","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"李璨琛，又名李燦森，原名李瑋璁，香港電影演員。代表作品包括《香港製造》、《特警新人類》、《狗咬狗》等。並曾跟 Ketchup 合作；現時也是 DJ，代號 DJ Becareful。","name":"李燦森","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Lý Xán Sâm","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Сэм Ли","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Sam Lee","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Сем Лі","primary":false}}]}},"person_3021181_translations":{"at":1773688734375,"data":{"id":3021181,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"　　中国内陆青年演员、模特，北京乐漾影视传媒有限公司旗下艺人，曾参演《萌妃驾到》。参与爱奇艺“天鹅计划”成功入选武侠轻喜剧《恋恋江湖》。","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Xu Kaixin","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Xu Kaixin","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Сюй Кай Синь","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"中國內陸青年演員、模特，北京樂漾影視傳媒有限公司旗下藝人，曾參演《萌妃駕到》。參與愛奇藝“天鵝計劃”成功入選武俠輕喜劇《戀戀江湖》。","name":"徐凱鑫","primary":false}}]}},"person_558015_translations":{"at":1773688738510,"data":{"id":558015,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Vladimir Simonov","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"Родился в городе Октябрьск, Куйбышевская область, РСФСР, СССР. Окончил Театральное училище имени Б.В. Щукина в 1980 году и был принят в МХАТ. В 1988 перешел в труппу театра имени Евгения Вахтангова. Участвовал в спектаклях Театра им. К.С.Станиславского, Театра Наций, театра \"Et cetera\". Снимается в фильмах. Работал с такими режиссерами, как М. Швейцер, А. Эфрос, П. Фоменко, И. Дыховичный. Заслуженный артист РФ (1995). Народный артист РФ (2001).","name":"Владимир Симонов","primary":true}}]}}}}